OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry for many
OL,6,Fthis evening. Clear spells overnight,
OL,7,Fespecially in the east with some mist
OL,8,Fand fog patches forming. However, the
OL,9,Fcloud will be thick enough to give
OL,10,Fsome drizzle further west. More
OL,11,Fpersistent rain arriving in the
OL,12,Fnorthwest later.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FRain will move southeast
OL,15,Facross Scotland and Northern Ireland,
OL,16,Fwith brisk winds. Brighter in the
OL,17,Fnorthwest later. England and Wales
OL,18,Fmostly dry and cloudy, but occasional
OL,19,Fbright intervals and mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
